g.text: The workspace confirmation flow is presented to the user in sequential steps, having users first confirm that they selected their desired location, the confirming that they have selected the desired time.
After the user confirms that they have selected the correct location, the button are displayed as disabled and the Date and Time Confirmation prompt appears.
Within the Date+Time confirmation, the information is presented as cards that the user can easily identify and adjust. If an incorrect date has been chose, the user can delete it.
